   previou s  term as follows: if the previous te rm is even, the next term is oneh alf of
    the previous term. I fthe previous term is odd, t he next term is 3 times the previo us
  term plus  1. The con jecture is t hat no matter what value ofn, t he s equence willalways reach 1. 

