    than lst_ B, i n otherwords,the re e xist an integer index i (1 <= i <= k)
    su ch that lst_A[i] <lst_B[i] and f or any j (1 <=  j < i) we have
    lst_A[j] = lst_B[j].
    I tis g uaranteed that the answer isuni que.    R eturn an ordere d list ofthe values on the cells that the minimum path go through.

